&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solaris&lt;/strong&gt; is Europe&#39;s leading embedded finance platform. Solaris’ full German banking license and proprietary modular B2B tech stack empowers its partners – from SMEs to large, multinational, non-financial companies – to offer compliant, customer-centric banking services, providing seamless experiences to customers across all industries. Founded in 2016, Solaris pioneered the Banking-as-a-Service market with an unparalleled combination of tech and banking. Solaris is headquartered in Berlin and employs 300 people in Europe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Your Role&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manual Underwriting Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and refine the structure of complex credit transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess and approve credit transactions, ensuring full compliance with the OHB (Operational Handbook) and external regulatory frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously perform, optimize, and maintain the credit approval process to enhance efficiency and accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain manual credit file management systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct regular reviews and updates of credit files to reflect current risk profiles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automatic Underwriting &amp;amp; Logic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in setting and refining the technical criteria for the Decision Engine.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align the conceptual consistency of underwriting principles across both manual and automated channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Credit Portfolio Steering&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare regular qualitative portfolio reviews accompanied by action proposals to maintain credit risk exposure within established risk appetite levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute ad-hoc assessments as required to mitigate emerging risks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor partnership team activities specifically regarding dunning, workout, and collection actions to ensure alignment with risk standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Projects &amp;amp; Compliance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take responsibility for closing audit findings within the respective focus areas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead training initiatives for CRM and Solaris staff on core underwriting principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive project-related tasks, including the development and launch of new loan products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
